Usage: attachTerm [-help] <instName> <termName> <netName>
                  [-moduleBased <moduleName>] [-noNewPort]
                  [-pin <refInstName> <refTermName>] [-port <portName>]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
<instName>                           # Name of Inst (string, required)
<termName>                           # Name of Term (string, required)
<netName>                            # Name of Net (string, required)
-moduleBased <moduleName>            # Name of verilog module
                                     # (string, optional)
-noNewPort                           # do not create new port if net did not
                                     # exist at hierarchy of term (bool, optional)
-pin <refInstName> <refTermName>     # Using the hterm that used for the
                                     # refInst term to do the connection.
                                     # (string, optional)
-port <portName>                     # Name of Port on module containing
                                     # instance (string, optional)